name: Aerial view weekacura waterfall, Sumba island, Indonesia
description:
Weekacura Waterfall is one of the waterfall tourist destinations in West Sumba. Weekacura waterfall has its own uniqueness because this waterfall is in the middle of rice fields. Although the Weekacura waterfall is in the area between the rice fields, this waterfall has very clear water.

Weekacura waterfall has several pools whose water is so clear. This place is perfect for those of you who want to relax and unwind. Apart from that because of the clarity of the water, this place is also instagramable for those of you who like to take pictures and can also be used for swimming.
